<!-- Page Title -->
<section class="s-page-title">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title-page">Shipping Policy</h1>
            <ul class="breadcrumbs-page">
                <li><a asp-page="/Index" class="h6 link">Home</a></li>
                <li class="d-flex"><i class="icon icon-caret-right"></i></li>
                <li><h6 class="current-page fw-normal">Shipping Policy</h6></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- /Page Title -->

<!-- Content -->
<section class="flat-spacing">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-9">
                <div class="policy-content">
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-4">Delivery, Cancellation &amp; Refund</h2>

                    <p><strong>Shipping Methods:</strong> We are well-timed for transport. Cancellation of merchandise: Note that cancellation is only possible if video evidence of the damaged merchandise is submitted within 48 hours; otherwise, it may not be processed.</p>

                    <p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> After receiving your order, we process and prepare it for shipping. Processing includes verifying your order, quality checks, packaging, and handover to the delivery partner. Expected processing time: <strong>0–4 working days</strong>.</p>

                    <p><strong>Shipping Time:</strong> Estimated delivery time after dispatch: <strong>7–10 working days</strong>. This may vary based on your location and selected shipping method.</p>

                    <p><strong>Tracking:</strong> For most orders, we provide a tracking number so you can monitor your shipment. You will receive an email with tracking details once your order is dispatched.</p>

                    <p><strong>International Shipping:</strong> We ship worldwide to select countries. All international orders may be subject to customs duties, taxes, and other government-imposed charges, which are the recipient's sole responsibility. Please contact your local customs office for more information.</p>

                    <p><strong>Shipping Restrictions:</strong> Some products may have shipping restrictions imposed by local authorities or carriers. If your item or destination has any such restrictions, we will contact you to discuss alternatives.</p>

                    <p><strong>Delivery Issues:</strong> If there is an issue with your delivery (lost or delayed), please contact our customer service team immediately. We will work with the courier to resolve the matter promptly.</p>

                    <p><strong>Shipping Costs:</strong> Shipping costs are calculated based on weight, dimensions, destination, and chosen shipping method. Applicable charges will be shown during checkout before you confirm your order.</p>

                    <p><strong>Free Shipping:</strong> We offer free standard shipping on orders above <strong>₹3,000</strong>. Orders below this threshold have a flat shipping fee of ₹80.</p>

                    <p><strong>Changes to Shipping Policy:</strong> We reserve the right to update our shipping policy at any time. Any revisions will be reflected on this page, so we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>

                    <div class="mt-40 text-center">
                        <p class="h6">Have questions about your order?</p>
                        <a asp-page="/contactus" class="tf-btn animate-btn mt-3">Contact Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- /Content -->